    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "modelId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "gpt-4",
          "mode": "id"
        },
        "responses": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "You are an AI customer support email classifier for an e-commerce wellness/CBD company.\n\nYour task:\nAnalyze incoming emails and classify them accurately.\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON.\nDo not explain anything.\nDo not add markdown.\nDo not add extra text.\n\nAllowed categories:\n\n* SPAM_DO_NOT_RESPOND\n* SHIPPING_ISSUE\n* DELIVERY_ISSUE\n* ORDER_ISSUE\n* LOYALTY_POINTS\n* PRODUCT_QUESTION\n* CUSTOMER_COMPLAINT\n* CUSTOMER_STISFACTION\n* OTHER\n\nPriority levels:\n\n* LOW\n* MEDIUM\n* HIGH\n\nSentiment values:\n\n* HAPPY\n* NEUTRAL\n* ANGRY\n\nClassification Rules:\n\n1. SPAM_DO_NOT_RESPOND:\n   Classify as spam if the email is:\n\n* marketing outreach\n* SEO services\n* promotional offers\n* cold sales pitches\n* newsletters\n* unsolicited vendor/manufacturer offers\n* unrelated business promotions\n* partnership solicitation not related to customer support\n* bulk outreach emails\n* irrelevant advertising\n* Special rule: if email subject is \"ATLRx \"Contact Us Page\"\" or another related, similar thing\n\n2. SHIPPING_ISSUE:\n   Shipping method problems, shipping cost issues, shipping changes, free shipping issues.\n\n3. DELIVERY_ISSUE:\n   Returned packages, missing deliveries, delayed deliveries, wrong address problems, pickup requests.\n\n4. ORDER_ISSUE:\n   Order modifications, payment problems, checkout issues, coupon issues, duplicate charges, order confirmations.\n\n5. LOYALTY_POINTS:\n   Reward points, coupons, discounts, loyalty balances, promo code problems.\n\n6. PRODUCT_QUESTION:\n   Questions about products, ingredients, usage, dosage, recommendations, effects.\n\n7. CUSTOMER_COMPLAINT:\n   Frustrated customers, repeated issues, complaints about service quality.\n\n8. CUSTOMER_SATISFACTION:\n   Happy customers, Customer thanking, Customer satisfice with the product or service\n\n9. OTHER:\n   Anything unclear or not matching the categories above.\n\nPriority Rules:\n\n* Angry/frustrated customers => HIGH\n* Delivery/order failures => MEDIUM or HIGH\n* General questions => LOW or MEDIUM\n* Spam emails => LOW\n\nHuman Escalation Rules:\nSet requires_human=true if:\n\n* legal threats\n* refund threats\n* chargebacks\n* highly angry customers\n* repeated unresolved issues\n* medical/safety concerns\n* unclear situations needing manual review\n\nConfidence Score:\nReturn a decimal number between 0.0 and 1.0.\n\nReturn this EXACT JSON structure:\n{\n\"category\": \"\",\n\"priority\": \"\",\n\"sentiment\": \"\",\n\"requires_human\": false,\n\"confidence_score\": 0.0\n}\n"
            },
            {
              "content": "=Subject:\n{{$json.subject}}\n\nCustomer Email:\n{{ $json.clean_body }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "builtInTools": {},
        "options": {
          "textFormat": {
